**File:** `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\components\ProfilePage\myprofile.css`

#### 3a. Base Widget Card (line 833-845)

Change `.profile-widget-card` from:
```css
.profile-widget-card{
    position: absolute;
    width: fit-content;
    max-width: min(100%, 520px);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
