**Changes explained:**
- `border-radius`: 12px to 16px (softer, more rounded per reference)
- `border`: switched to `--border-widget` for the warm-toned border
- `background-color`: switched from `--bg-glass` to `--bg-widget-card` (warm cream, solid)
